rdnCableSpectrumGroup.name: rdnCableSpectrumGroup
rdnCableSpectrumGroup.contactinfo: Motorola Customer Service Postal: Motorola Three Highwood Dr east Tewksbury, MA 01876 U.S.A. Tel: +1 978 858 2300 E-mail: BSRSNMP@maillist2001.mot.com
rdnCableSpectrumGroup.description: This is the MIB Module for Cable Spectrum Group Management for MCNS compliant Cable Modem Termination Systems (CMTS).

SpecDataArray.name: SpecDataArray
SpecDataArray.description: An array holds the spectrum data.

rdnSpectrumGroupTable.name: rdnSpectrumGroupTable
rdnSpectrumGroupTable.description: This table keeps the records of spectrum groups. These groups can be configured and activated by the spectrum manager and used by the CMTS upstream port for frequency hopping.

rdnSpectrumGroupEntry.name: rdnSpectrumGroupEntry
rdnSpectrumGroupEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumGroupEntry. An entry in this table exists for each spectrum group that has been configured by the spectrum manager.

rdnSpectrumGroupName.name: rdnSpectrumGroupName
rdnSpectrumGroupName.description: The text name (index) of the spectrum group.

rdnSpectrumGroupId.name: rdnSpectrumGroupId
rdnSpectrumGroupId.description: The number index for the spectrum group.

rdnSpectrumGroupHopPeriod.name: rdnSpectrumGroupHopPeriod
rdnSpectrumGroupHopPeriod.description: The rate at which the frequency hop takes place. This would be useful in preventing excessive hops. Unit is in second.

rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdFlap.name: rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdFlap
rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdFlap.description: The CM flap rate percentage threshold that controls the hopping frequency. The hopping only happens when the percentage of flap CMs is higher than this threshold. Value 0 means the flap threshold hop disabled

rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdError.name: rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdError
rdnSpectrumGroupHopThresholdError.description: The FEC error rate percentage threshold that controls the hopping frequency. The hopping only happens when the error rate percentage is higher than this threshold. The unit is 1/1000.

rdnSpectrumGroupHopRollbackEnable.name: rdnSpectrumGroupHopRollbackEnable
rdnSpectrumGroupHopRollbackEnable.description: This field controls the spectrum rollback option when the original channel quality recovers. The rollback is allowed when this field is enabled. The rollback is not allowed when this field is set to disable.

rdnSpectrumDataCollectResolution.name: rdnSpectrumDataCollectResolution
rdnSpectrumDataCollectResolution.description: The spectrum data collection resolution, in Hz.

rdnSpectrumDataCollectInterval.name: rdnSpectrumDataCollectInterval
rdnSpectrumDataCollectInterval.description: The spectrum data collection interval, in second. Minimum value 60 seconds. Value 0 means the collection is disabled.

rdnSpectrumGroupGuardBand.name: rdnSpectrumGroupGuardBand
rdnSpectrumGroupGuardBand.description: The minimum spectrum separation between upstream channels in the same spectrum group, in Hz.

rdnSpectrumGroupRowStatus.name: rdnSpectrumGroupRowStatus
rdnSpectrumGroupRowStatus.description: Controls and reflects the status of rows in this table. This field is used to control the addition and deletion of a spectrum group.

rdnOfflineModemCount.name: rdnOfflineModemCount
rdnOfflineModemCount.description: Number of offline modems for this spectrum group

rdnOnlineModemCount.name: rdnOnlineModemCount
rdnOnlineModemCount.description: Number of online modems for this spectrum group

rdnActiveModemCount.name: rdnActiveModemCount
rdnActiveModemCount.description: Number of active modems for this spectrum group

rdnRegisteredModemCount.name: rdnRegisteredModemCount
rdnRegisteredModemCount.description: Number of registered modems for this spectrum group

rdnProvisionedModemCount.name: rdnProvisionedModemCount
rdnProvisionedModemCount.description: Number of provisioned modems for this spectrum group

rdnUnregisteredModemCount.name: rdnUnregisteredModemCount
rdnUnregisteredModemCount.description: Number of Unregistered modems for this spectrum group

rdnSpectrumBandSchedTable.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedTable
rdnSpectrumBandSchedTable.description: This table keeps the records of spectrum band scheduled for a specific spectrum group.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedEntry.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedEntry
rdnSpectrumBandSchedEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumBandScheEntry.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedId.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedId
rdnSpectrumBandSchedId.description: The identifier for the band schedule, it is the second index for the spectrum band schedule table.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedAction.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedAction
rdnSpectrumBandSchedAction.description: The action on the specified frequency band. The third index of this band schedule table. Band add (1), band delete (2).

rdnSpectrumBandFreqLow.name: rdnSpectrumBandFreqLow
rdnSpectrumBandFreqLow.description: The spectrum band low frequency in Hz. The lower bound is 5 MHz for North American standard, is 5 MHz for European standard.

rdnSpectrumBandFreqHigh.name: rdnSpectrumBandFreqHigh
rdnSpectrumBandFreqHigh.description: The spectrum band high frequency in Hz. This value must be at least 200000 Hz higher than the band low frequency. The upper bound is 42 MHz for North American standard, is 65 MHz for European standard.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedWeekDay.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedWeekDay
rdnSpectrumBandSchedWeekDay.description: The week day of the band schedule.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedHour.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedHour
rdnSpectrumBandSchedHour.description: The hour of the band schedule (in 24-hour format).

rdnSpectrumBandSchedMinute.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedMinute
rdnSpectrumBandSchedMinute.description: The minute of the band schedule.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedSecond.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedSecond
rdnSpectrumBandSchedSecond.description: The second of the band schedule.

rdnSpectrumBandSchedRowStatus.name: rdnSpectrumBandSchedRowStatus
rdnSpectrumBandSchedRowStatus.description: The row status that controls the addition and deletion of the band schedule entry.

rdnSpectrumHopTable.name: rdnSpectrumHopTable
rdnSpectrumHopTable.description: This table keeps the records of spectrum hopping rules for a specific spectrum group.

rdnSpectrumHopEntry.name: rdnSpectrumHopEntry
rdnSpectrumHopEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumHopTable.

rdnSpectrumHopId.name: rdnSpectrumHopId
rdnSpectrumHopId.description: The index for the spectrum hop rule table.

rdnSpectrumHopSelection.name: rdnSpectrumHopSelection
rdnSpectrumHopSelection.description: Identifies the selection of the action for this spectrum hop rule.

rdnSpectrumHopPriority.name: rdnSpectrumHopPriority
rdnSpectrumHopPriority.description: Identifies the priority for this spectrum hop policy. The default value is 128. The range is 1 to 255.

rdnSpectrumHopFrequency.name: rdnSpectrumHopFrequency
rdnSpectrumHopFrequency.description: Identifies the center frequency for the spectrum hop schedule entry. The hop can be specified with a discrete center frequency or with a band but not both in the same group.

rdnSpectrumHopBandLow.name: rdnSpectrumHopBandLow
rdnSpectrumHopBandLow.description: The start frequency for the individual spectrum hop.

rdnSpectrumHopBandHigh.name: rdnSpectrumHopBandHigh
rdnSpectrumHopBandHigh.description: The stop frequency for the individual spectrum hop. This value must be at least 200000 Hz higher than the start frequency.

rdnSpectrumHopChannelWidth.name: rdnSpectrumHopChannelWidth
rdnSpectrumHopChannelWidth.description: Identifies the channel width change for this individual spectrum hop. The valid band width is 200000 Hz, 400000 Hz, 800000 Hz, 1600000 Hz, 3200000 Hz

rdnSpectrumHopPowerLevel.name: rdnSpectrumHopPowerLevel
rdnSpectrumHopPowerLevel.description: Identifies a power level change for this individual spectrum hop. Different channel width has different power level range, < -160, 140 > for 200 KHz, < -130, 170 > for 400 KHz, < -100, 200 > for 800 KHz, < -70, 230 > for 1600 KHz, < -40, 260 > for 3200 KHz. For power default, the range is < -150, 150 > for all the channel widths. The unit is in tenths of a dBmV.

rdnSpectrumHopModulationProfile.name: rdnSpectrumHopModulationProfile
rdnSpectrumHopModulationProfile.description: Identifies the modulation profile change for this individual spectrum hop.

rdnSpectrumHopRowStatus.name: rdnSpectrumHopRowStatus
rdnSpectrumHopRowStatus.description: The row status that controls the add and deletion of the spectrum hop rule entry.

rdnSpectrumMemberChannelTable.name: rdnSpectrumMemberChannelTable
rdnSpectrumMemberChannelTable.description: This table keeps the records of the associations between upstream channels and spectrum groups

rdnSpectrumMemberChannelEntry.name: rdnSpectrumMemberChannelEntry
rdnSpectrumMemberChannelEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the RdnSpectrumMemberChannelEntry. It is indexed by ifIndex.

rdnMemChSpectrumGroupId.name: rdnMemChSpectrumGroupId
rdnMemChSpectrumGroupId.description: The ID for the spectrum group that is associated with this upstream channel. Value 0 means no association.

rdnMemChSpectrumGroupName.name: rdnMemChSpectrumGroupName
rdnMemChSpectrumGroupName.description: The text name of the associated spectrum group.

rdnSpectrumDataTable.name: rdnSpectrumDataTable
rdnSpectrumDataTable.description: This table stores the noise and error rate for the different frequency bands.

rdnSpectrumDataEntry.name: rdnSpectrumDataEntry
rdnSpectrumDataEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumDataEntry.

rdnSpectrumDataIndex.name: rdnSpectrumDataIndex
rdnSpectrumDataIndex.description: The internal index of the spectrum data

rdnSpectrumDataStartFrequency.name: rdnSpectrumDataStartFrequency
rdnSpectrumDataStartFrequency.description: Start Frequency of the spectrum data collection

rdnSpectrumDataResolution.name: rdnSpectrumDataResolution
rdnSpectrumDataResolution.description: Resolution of the spectrum data collection in Hz

rdnSpectrumDataSamples.name: rdnSpectrumDataSamples
rdnSpectrumDataSamples.description: Number of data samples used in this spectrum data collection period

rdnSpectrumDataLastUpdate.name: rdnSpectrumDataLastUpdate
rdnSpectrumDataLastUpdate.description: Date and time when this collection data was last updated

rdnSpectrumDataArray.name: rdnSpectrumDataArray
rdnSpectrumDataArray.description: The data array that holds the spectrum data.

rdnSpectrumQualityTable.name: rdnSpectrumQualityTable
rdnSpectrumQualityTable.description: This table stores the spectrum quality information.

rdnSpectrumQualityEntry.name: rdnSpectrumQualityEntry
rdnSpectrumQualityEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumDataEntry.

rdnSpecQualityUsChId.name: rdnSpecQualityUsChId
rdnSpecQualityUsChId.description: Identifies the upstream channel id for which the spectrum signal quality is gathered.

rdnSpectrumQualityDataLastUpdate.name: rdnSpectrumQualityDataLastUpdate
rdnSpectrumQualityDataLastUpdate.description: Date and time when this data was last updated

rdnSpectrumDataInBandPower.name: rdnSpectrumDataInBandPower
rdnSpectrumDataInBandPower.description: The in-band power for this frequency band. The unit is the tenths of dBmV.

rdnSpectrumTotCodeWord.name: rdnSpectrumTotCodeWord
rdnSpectrumTotCodeWord.description: The total number of code words transfer through this interface

rdnSpectrumErrorCodeWord.name: rdnSpectrumErrorCodeWord
rdnSpectrumErrorCodeWord.description: The uncorrectable error code words received through this interface.

rdnSpectrumMapTable.name: rdnSpectrumMapTable
rdnSpectrumMapTable.description: This table keeps the records of spectrum usage.

rdnSpectrumMapEntry.name: rdnSpectrumMapEntry
rdnSpectrumMapEntry.description: List of attributes for an entry in the rdnSpectrumMapEntry.

rdnSpectrumMapIndex.name: rdnSpectrumMapIndex
rdnSpectrumMapIndex.description: Identifies an entry in the spectrum map table

rdnSpectrumMapStartFrequency.name: rdnSpectrumMapStartFrequency
rdnSpectrumMapStartFrequency.description: The start frequency of the current spectrum band.

rdnSpectrumMapStopFrequency.name: rdnSpectrumMapStopFrequency
rdnSpectrumMapStopFrequency.description: The stop frequency of the current spectrum band.

rdnSpectrumMapStatus.name: rdnSpectrumMapStatus
rdnSpectrumMapStatus.description: The spectrum band status. null (0), available (1), occupied (2), admin-down (3)
